<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Grace Engineering - Home</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset default margin and padding */
    body, h1, p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Set background color and text styles */
    body {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Header styles */
    header {
      background-color: #222;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h3 {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    /* Main content styles */
    .container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Call to action button styles */
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 18px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #555;
    }

    /* Footer styles */
    footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #222;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Grace Engineering</h1>
    <h3>Your trusted partner in engineering solutions</h3>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Grace Engineering under a forward looking management foresees the organization as not only the leading trading and manufacturing Company of the country, but also as a company known for its people, partnerships and performance in the region.</p>
    <p>The Company continued with its strategies of accelerating business in Dairy, Pharmaceutical, Chemical, Cement, Power Generation and allied industries.</p>
    <p>Company has gained lot of useful experience in dairy and confectionary industry and specially in cheese industry.</p>
    <a class="cta-button" href="http://www.azharco.com/">Get Started</a>
    <a class="cta-button" href="<%= view_inventories_path %>" onclick="navigateToInventory(event, href)">Inventory</a>
    <a class="cta-button" href="<%= view_productions_path %>" onclick="navigateToInventory(event, href)">Production</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    // No changes made to the JavaScript code
    function navigateToInventory(event, href) {
      event.preventDefault(); // Prevent the default link behavior

      // Set the URL of the inventory page
      var inventoryUrl = href;

      // Reload the page by navigating to the inventory URL
      window.location.href = inventoryUrl;
    }
  </script>

  <footer>
    &copy;2023 Grace Engineering.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
